reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Size is not accurate .
reviews.reviewText: This was a Christmas toy for my grandson. He loves the dinosaurs and they seem to be made well but they are way smaller than they appear this ad.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value and assortment
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this product for a charity event for underprivileged children. The children requested one thing they really wanted and the 3 year old I pulled wanted dinosaurs. This set was perfect. He LOVED it and was ecstatic at the amount of items that came in the little case. He kept pulling dinosaurs out and giggling. Great quality and brought so much joy when needed most. I would highly suggest for any child that loves dinosaurs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is so fun. The dinosaur are fun (though a few are flimsy and don’t want to stay up), the mat is fun (though small but we knew that when we bought it) it’s fine for one person or two smaller people, the dinosaur cars are the best part which is why we bought this one. Everybody loves the dinosaur cars.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Love the idea and it comes in a nice case to carry everything. It is a LOT smaller than in pictures which is deceiving! This is ONLY reason I gave 4 stars. It would have been 5 otherwise. The dinosaurs and parts inside are small so I don’t recommend it for children under age 3. My grandson who I bought it for is 2 so might save it for his birthday. Otherwise it’s a very nice toy set.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My nephew got this as a gift and he absolutely love it, it comes with a mat and he loves playing with all of them. I also love how it comes with a box to put them away, when he’s done playing with them. Easy clean up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These roll really good
reviews.reviewText: I got these cute little critters for my grand daughter at Christmas. They are bigger and more chunkier, so easy for her to grasp.She can sit on the floor and play with them, they roll very easy backwards or forward. There is a lot of critters in the set, all different kinds of cute animals.I also like that there is a storage box to put them up in, after play. She is enjoying play with them, she is 1 year old.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Don’t let the ad photo fool you.
reviews.reviewText: The photo for the listing is inaccurate. It’s a small set, the size of a small tool chest or makeup case. The dinos are plenty but small as well. If the photo had been honest it would’ve been a perfect review, it’s perfect if you are looking for small. Check out my photo next to bananas.
